text.section:
The executive director shall be responsible for:
Collecting and depositing into the fund all fees submitted by permittees;
Assessing permit eligibility of permittees for late payment or nonpayment of fees, in accordance with KRS 350.515 and 350.518;
Compiling information about permittees for use by the commission in assigning or revising classifications and fees;
Paying moneys out of the fund as authorized by the commission;
At each meeting of the commission, reporting to the same, the status of the fund and activities of the fund's executive director; and
Performing other administrative functions as are necessary to carry out the purposes of KRS 350.500 to 350.521.
